Key Match Events: Jordan Ayew scored a late winner for Ghana in their 2-1 victory over Mali in the 2026 FIFA World Cup qualifiers at the Stade du 26 Mars in Bamako on Thursday, June 6, 2024.
Kamory Doumbia scored the opener for Mali in added time of the first half.
Ernest Nuamah scored the equalizer for Ghana after a cross from Salis Samed.
